originalText.text: Dr. Anne Mooney is an exceptional and outstanding doctor and person. She shows compassion and I also brilliance in her work and ethics. I have never met a better person in the entire field of medical care than her to this day and I sincerely do not think I ever will! Never have I met someone so helpful, kind, and overall just terrific as her.

originalText.text: There are Doctors that have a medical degree and therefore practice medicine. But it takes a special human being to truly reflect the most highest of standards in medical care; but also have compassion, approach-ability and exceptional insights into how patients that have an illness must feel. Dr. Anne Mooney is one of those exceptional Doctors and human beings that actually makes a difference for her patients. My wife has been under Dr. Mooney’s care for over three years, and she never seems to amaze us. She is caring, thoughtful, brilliant and every matter to her is handled in urgency. If anyone has a sleeping disorder they must go nowhere except to see Dr. Anne Mooney….you will never be disappointed!!!
